Class CarbonExtension.Private

  • java.lang.Object

    CarbonExtension

    public static class CarbonExtension.Private
extends Object
implements PacketExtension
    Packet extension indicating that a message may not be carbon-copied. Adding this extension to any message will disallow that message from being copied.
